data.description: FYI A quality craftsman log home like this cost approximately 25% more to build verses a standard conventional stick framed home.  Come see this Elegant, but Rustic Custom Log Home with ALL the upgrades! This is the Cadillac of log homes. Enjoy the local mountain views, look and listen to 600’ of Wolf Creek from the MASSIVE Log covered deck that features outdoor fireplace, bar, plenty of seating and spa extraordinaire!! Front yard waterfall, Oversized garage, 10'x50' porch, expansive covered patio and second 10' x 30' covered balcony. Low maintenance drip systems through out property. Oversized 10" logs with huge open beam. Jenn-air Commercial Refrigerator, counter tops and high-end appliances. Beautifully appointed upstairs master spacious bdrm., split zone Heat & Air systems. May heat/air only master bedroom and TV sitting area. 10' x 40' storage under patio. Orchard 25+ trees and vineyards. Two 12’ x 30 creekside cement patios. 16.4K solar system off sets a monthly $600. + PG&E bill. 60’ paved RV pad. stairlift, VA  2.25% assumable loan.  Lanterns LED lighting to and along entire creek.  MUCH, MUCH, MORE.
